SUMMARY:Improv Unexpected at Jules Maes in Georgetown
DESCRIPTION:Improv comes to Georgetown! Seattle’s legendary improv company\, Unexpected Productions\, brings you the Improv Unexpected. The talented cast members take your suggestions and spontaneously create hilarious stories\, zany scenes\, and fun songs right on the spot and in the moment just for YOU! \n21+ with valid ID. All sales are non-refundable. If the event is rescheduled\, all purchases will be honored for the next event date. If the event is canceled\, all purchases will be refunded in full
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/improv-unexpected-at-jules-maes-in-georgetown-8-2-2-2/2026-03-31/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike Place Market\, Seattle\, WA\, 98101\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jules-Maes-small.jpg
END:VEVENT
